StructureDefinition-aqr

source file: source/pages/_includes/aqr-intro.md

The Argonaut Adaptive QR profile is derived from the Argonaut QR profile requiring a containedArgonaut Questionnaire Profile to support the adaptive questionnaire use case. This profile defines the structure that is passed between the Client and Server using the $next-q operation and records the question-answer pairs and questionnaire questions from the adaptive questionnaire.
